Class ComparableRectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • GeometricObject
      • ComparableRectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<GeometricObject>

    public class ComparableRectangle
extends GeometricObject
    The following class is used to build a rectangle that can be compared, implementing the abstract methods in the geometric object class and the comparable interface.
